  <!-- FAQs Widget ******************* -->

  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="Here are some of the most common questions we get asked about our services. If you have any other questions, feel free to reach out."
    tagline="FAQs"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'What is Nudge The Web?',
        description:
          "Nudge The Web is a Sydney based digital marketing and operational enhancement agency that helps businesses grow through targeted marketing and strategic scaling. Our team of experts works with you to identify key performance indicators and optimize your business's growth potential.",
      },
      {
        title: 'What services does Nudge The Web offer?',
        description:
          'We offer a range of services designed to help your business grow, including digital marketing, operational enhancements, and strategic scaling. Our team of experts will work with you to identify key performance indicators and develop a tailored strategy to help you achieve your business goals.',
      },
      {
        title: 'What is the process for working with Nudge The Web?',
        description:
          'The first step in working with Nudge The Web is to schedule a consultation with one of our experts. During this consultation, we will discuss your business goals and objectives and develop a tailored strategy to help you achieve them. Once we have a clear understanding of your business needs, we will work with you to implement the strategy and help your business grow.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How can I get started with Nudge The Web?',
        description:
          'To get started with Nudge The Web, simply schedule a consultation with one of our experts. During this consultation, we will discuss your business goals and objectives and develop a tailored strategy to help you achieve them. Once we have a clear understanding of your business needs, we will work with you to implement the strategy and help your business grow.',
      },
      
    ]}
  />

